---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Chris wird 50">

  <!-- ==================== HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="section min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Hero background photo — super saturated / verfremdet -->
    <img src="/photos/strandperle_hamburg.jpg" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" style="filter: saturate(2.5) contrast(1.15) brightness(1.05); transform: scale(1.1) translateZ(0); will-change: transform; contain: strict;" loading="eager" />
    <!-- Color tint glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(194,112,62,0.2) 0%, rgba(120,60,180,0.08) 50%, transparent 80%);"></div>
    <!-- Subtle vignette -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 40%, rgba(26,29,46,0.25) 100%);"></div>
    <!-- Bottom fade for transition -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-transparent to-[#f4f1ec]/70"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10">

      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#1a1d2e] inline-block">
          <span style="background: rgba(244,241,236,0.8); padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 4px; box-decoration-break: clone; -webkit-box-decoration-break: clone;">Chris wird 50</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-[#2a2d3a]">
          <span style="background: rgba(244,241,236,0.7); padding: 2px 12px; border-radius: 3px;">Halbes Jahrhundert. Kein Grund zur Panik.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Countdown -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <div id="countdown" class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2" style="background: rgba(244,241,236,0.75); padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px;">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <span id="cd-days" class="cd-digit">000</span>
          <span class="cd-label">Tage</span>
        </div>
        <span class="cd-sep">:</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <span id="cd-hours" class="cd-digit">00</span>
          <span class="cd-label">Std</span>
        </div>
        <span class="cd-sep">:</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <span id="cd-minutes" class="cd-digit">00</span>
          <span class="cd-label">Min</span>
        </div>
        <span class="cd-sep">:</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <span id="cd-seconds" class="cd-digit">00</span>
          <span class="cd-label">Sek</span>
        </div>
        </div>
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#8b8fa3] uppercase tracking-widest">Party Timer</span>
      </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll hint -->
        <div class="w-px h-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-[#1a1d2e]/15 mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== DETAILS ==================== -->
  <section class="section py-32 md:py-40">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-16">

      <!-- Greeting -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="accent-line mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-relaxed text-[#2a2d3a]">
          Ich werde 50. Lasst uns das feiern. Mit gutem Essen, guten Drinks, guter Musik und vor allem...mit euch!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick info -->
      <div>
        <div class="card card-hover p-8 space-y-4 max-w-md">
          <p class="mono-label">Wann</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-medium text-[#1a1d2e]">
            19. September 2026
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8b8fa3]">Ab 15:00 Uhr — Treffpunkt Strandperle</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== PROGRAMM + MAP ==================== -->
  <section class="section py-24 md:py-32" id="programm">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="accent-line mb-6"></div>
        <p class="mono-label mb-3">Auf einen Blick</p>
        <h2 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Das Programm</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] mt-3">Von der Elbe durch den Hafen in die Küche. Fünf Stationen quer durch Hamburg.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
        <!-- Station Cards -->
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">

          <!-- Station 1: Strandperle -->
          <div class="card overflow-hidden" data-station="1">
            <div class="md:flex">
              <div class="md:w-2/5 h-48 md:h-auto relative">
                <img src="/photos/strandperle_hamburg.jpg" alt="Strandperle Hamburg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#E53935] flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                  <span class="text-white font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-semibold text-sm">1</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:w-3/5 space-y-2">
                <p class="font-mono text-[#c2703e] text-sm">15:00</p>
                <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Strandperle</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">Ankommen, Umtrunk, Füße in den Sand. Wir starten entspannt am schönsten Strand Hamburgs.</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-[#8b8fa3]">Övelgönne 60, 22605 Hamburg</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Station 2: Zum Anleger -->
          <div class="card overflow-hidden" data-station="2">
            <div class="md:flex">
              <div class="md:w-2/5 h-48 md:h-auto relative">
                <img src="/photos/Museumshafen-Oevelgoenne-Hamburg.jfif" alt="Museumshafen Övelgönne" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#E53935] flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                  <span class="text-white font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-semibold text-sm">2</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:w-3/5 space-y-2">
                <p class="font-mono text-[#c2703e] text-sm">16:45</p>
                <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Spaziergang zum Anleger</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">Kurzer Spaziergang am Elbstrand entlang, vorbei am Museumshafen, zum Anleger Övelgönne.</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-[#8b8fa3]">Strandperle → Anleger Övelgönne</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Station 3: Barkasse -->
          <div class="card overflow-hidden" data-station="3">
            <div class="md:flex">
              <div class="md:w-2/5 h-48 md:h-auto relative">
                <img src="/photos/barkasse.jpg" alt="Barkassenfahrt auf der Elbe" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#E53935] flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                  <span class="text-white font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-semibold text-sm">3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:w-3/5 space-y-2">
                <p class="font-mono text-[#c2703e] text-sm">17:00</p>
                <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Barkassenfahrt</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">Mit der Barkasse über die Elbe Richtung Landungsbrücken — Hamburg von seiner besten Seite.</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-[#8b8fa3]">Anleger Övelgönne → Landungsbrücken, Brücke 1</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Station 4: Landungsbrücken -->
          <div class="card overflow-hidden" data-station="4">
            <div class="md:flex">
              <div class="md:w-2/5 h-48 md:h-auto relative">
                <img src="/photos/an-den-landungsbrucken.jpg" alt="Landungsbrücken Hamburg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#E53935] flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                  <span class="text-white font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-semibold text-sm">4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:w-3/5 space-y-2">
                <p class="font-mono text-[#c2703e] text-sm">18:30</p>
                <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Landungsbrücken</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">Ankunft Brücke 1. Dann zu Fuß durch die Hafengegend ins Portugiesenviertel.</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-[#8b8fa3]">Landungsbrücken, Brücke 1</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Station 5: La Cocina -->
          <div class="card overflow-hidden" data-station="5">
            <div class="md:flex">
              <div class="md:w-2/5 h-48 md:h-auto relative">
                <img src="/photos/LaCocina-Hamburg-11-683x1024-1.jpg" alt="La Cocina Hamburg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#E53935] flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                  <span class="text-white font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] font-semibold text-sm">5</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:w-3/5 space-y-2">
                <p class="font-mono text-[#c2703e] text-sm">19:00</p>
                <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-xl text-[#1a1d2e]">Küchenparty</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">La Cocina — gemeinsam kochen, essen, trinken. Keine Zuschauer, alle machen mit.</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-[#8b8fa3]">La Cocina, Ludwig-Erhard-Straße 37</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Fixed Map -->
        <div class="lg:w-[420px] flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-8">
            <div class="card overflow-hidden">
              <div id="map" class="w-full h-[350px] lg:h-[500px]"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== RSVP ==================== -->
  <section class="section py-24 md:py-32" id="rsvp">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="accent-line mb-6 mx-auto"></div>
        <p class="mono-label mb-3">Zusage</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#4a4d5e]">
          Sag kurz Bescheid, ob du dabei bist.
        </p>
      </div>

      <form id="rsvp-form" class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" name="Name" placeholder="Name" required class="form-input" />
        <input type="email" name="Email" placeholder="E-Mail" required class="form-input" />
        <select name="Dabei" required class="form-input">
          <option value="" disabled selected>Dabei?</option>
          <option value="Ja, bin dabei">Ja, bin dabei</option>
          <option value="Noch unsicher">Noch unsicher</option>
          <option value="Schaffe es leider nicht">Schaffe es leider nicht</option>
        </select>
        <input type="number" name="Personen" placeholder="Anzahl Personen gesamt (inkl. Dir)" min="1" max="10" class="form-input" />
        <select name="Ernaehrung" class="form-input">
          <option value="" disabled selected>Ernährung (optional)</option>
          <option value="Alles">Alles — keine Einschränkungen</option>
          <option value="Vegetarisch">Vegetarisch</option>
          <option value="Vegan">Vegan</option>
        </select>
        <textarea name="Unverträglichkeiten" placeholder="Allergien / Unverträglichkeiten (optional)" rows="2" class="form-input"></textarea>
        <textarea name="Nachricht" placeholder="Nachricht (optional)" rows="3" class="form-input"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full mt-2">
          Absenden
        </button>
        <p id="rsvp-status" class="text-center text-sm text-[#8b8fa3] hidden"></p>
      </form>

      <script>
        document.getElementById('rsvp-form')?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
          e.preventDefault();
          const form = e.target as HTMLFormElement;
          const btn = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]') as HTMLButtonElement;
          const status = document.getElementById('rsvp-status')!;
          
          btn.disabled = true;
          btn.textContent = 'Wird gesendet...';
          status.classList.add('hidden');

          const data: Record<string, string> = {};
          new FormData(form).forEach((v, k) => data[k] = v as string);

          try {
            const res = await fetch('/api/rsvp', {
              method: 'POST',
              headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
              body: JSON.stringify(data),
            });
            const result = await res.json();
            if (res.ok && result.result === 'ok') {
              status.textContent = 'Danke! Deine Antwort wurde gespeichert.';
              status.classList.remove('hidden');
              status.classList.remove('text-red-500');
              status.classList.add('text-[#c2703e]');
              form.reset();
            } else {
              throw new Error(result.message || 'Fehler');
            }
          } catch {
            status.textContent = 'Fehler beim Senden. Bitte versuch es nochmal.';
            status.classList.remove('hidden');
            status.classList.add('text-red-500');
          } finally {
            btn.disabled = false;
            btn.textContent = 'Absenden';
          }
        });
      </script>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== PLAYLISTS ==================== -->
  <section class="section py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-12">
      <div>
        <div class="accent-line mb-6"></div>
        <p class="mono-label mb-3">Playlists</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#4a4d5e]">
          Bau mit am Soundtrack.
          <br />Bitte füge Deine Tracks zu den kollaborativen Playlists hinzu.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Playlist 1: Boat, Cooking & Dinner -->
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#2a2d3a]">Barkasse, Kochen & Essen</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8fa3] mt-1">Füg Tracks hinzu, die zum Kochen, Essen und Zusammensein passen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-4" style="content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: auto 384px;">
          <div class="spotify-lazy" data-src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/5NrAL1envOg6jB4XX7R41y?utm_source=generator&theme=0" style="width:100%;height:352px;border-radius:12px;background:#282828;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Playlist 2: Party -->
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#2a2d3a]">Danach: Party</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8fa3] mt-1">Die Küche wird zur Tanzfläche. Pack rein, was Beine bewegt — alles erlaubt.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-4" style="content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: auto 384px;">
          <div class="spotify-lazy" data-src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/2xvNWJWODRYShVwJrthghu?utm_source=generator&theme=0" style="width:100%;height:352px;border-radius:12px;background:#282828;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <script>
        // Lazy-load Spotify iframes only when scrolled into view
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              const placeholder = entry.target as HTMLElement;
              const iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
              iframe.src = placeholder.dataset.src!;
              iframe.width = '100%';
              iframe.height = '352';
              iframe.frameBorder = '0';
              iframe.allow = 'autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture';
              iframe.loading = 'lazy';
              iframe.style.borderRadius = '12px';
              placeholder.replaceWith(iframe);
              observer.unobserve(entry.target);
            }
          });
        }, { rootMargin: '200px' });
        document.querySelectorAll('.spotify-lazy').forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
      </script>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== FAQ ==================== -->
  <section class="section py-24 md:py-32" id="faq">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <div class="accent-line mb-6"></div>
        <p class="mono-label mb-3">Fragen & Antworten</p>
        <h2 class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#1a1d2e] mb-12">FAQ</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-0">
        <!-- Dresscode -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Gibt es einen Dresscode?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Kommt so, wie ihr euch wohlfühlt. Wir sind den ganzen Tag draußen und am Wasser unterwegs — bequeme Schuhe sind wichtiger als schicke. Abends wird gekocht, nicht diniert.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Kinder -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Können Kinder mitkommen?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Am Elbstrand und auf der Barkasse sind Kinder herzlich willkommen! Beim Kochen abends bei La Cocina sind nur unsere eigenen Kids und ein paar wenige eng befreundete Kinder dabei — bitte habt Verständnis.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Anreise -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Wie komme ich zur Strandperle?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Mit dem ÖPNV: Bus 112 bis Haltestelle <strong>Neumühlen/Övelgönne</strong>, dann ca. 5 Minuten zu Fuß den Elbstrand entlang. Alternativ Fähre 62 ab Landungsbrücken bis <strong>Neumühlen</strong>. Unten am Strand gibt es keine Parkplätze — Autofahrer parken oben an der Elbchaussee.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Schlechtes Wetter -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Was passiert bei schlechtem Wetter?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Sollte das Wetter nicht mitspielen, fällt die Strandperle aus. Wir treffen uns dann stattdessen um <strong>17:00 Uhr direkt am Anleger Övelgönne</strong> und starten von dort mit der Barkasse. Ihr bekommt rechtzeitig Bescheid.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Treffpunkt 17h -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Kann ich auch erst um 17 Uhr dazustoßen?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Klar! Wer nicht schon um 15 Uhr an der Strandperle sein kann, kommt einfach um <strong>17:00 Uhr zum Anleger Övelgönne</strong>. Die Barkasse legt pünktlich ab — bitte seid ein paar Minuten vorher da. Vermerkt das bitte kurz im RSVP-Formular unter „Nachricht".
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Geschenke -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Sollen wir etwas mitbringen?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            Eure Anwesenheit ist das beste Geschenk. Wirklich. Wer trotzdem etwas beisteuern möchte — überrascht uns.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Dauer -->
        <details class="group border-b border-[#1a1d2e]/[0.06]">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between py-5 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk',sans-serif] text-lg text-[#1a1d2e] group-open:text-[#c2703e] transition-colors">Wie lange geht der Abend?</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[#8b8fa3] text-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-5 text-sm text-[#4a4d5e] leading-relaxed">
            La Cocina gehört uns für den ganzen Abend. Nach dem Kochen und Essen wird die Küche zur Tanzfläche. Open End — bleibt so lange ihr wollt.
          </div>
